{"tid":1108051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★拾荒婦聽羅致光建議求助勞工處　見工時填寫4頁表格後 職員就話請咗人","createTime":"2019-04-15T16:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T05:39:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6fbaee223ffadba03ae8f5f36067c31813a8a57b","tid":1108051,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:21:25.000Z","msg":"64歲的拾荒者「黃姐」，本月初到立法會出席福利事務委員會公聽會，向勞工及福利局長羅致光哭訴長者就業困難，獲羅致光以「可以搵勞工處協助就業」回覆，令她當場痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n「黃姐」事後聽從羅致光「建議」在勞工處介紹及安排下，等待半個月後獲得面試機會，於今日（15日）到公立醫院宿舍應徵清潔雜工，但無奈她未開始面試，職員已直言有關職位已聘到合適人選，令她感到相當無奈：「約我來，問都未問就話請咗人。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2683197/org/3d33a32e9bb1cfa6a0aed39c90436732.jpg/8Xfk_NOFduq8N3UeKjxn8S_Fy5dV0eXFnYWYc52FmHM?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2683197%2Forg%2F3d33a32e9bb1cfa6a0aed39c90436732.jpg%2F8Xfk_NOFduq8N3UeKjxn8S_Fy5dV0eXFnYWYc52FmHM%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=79e18a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關注拾荒者權益的團體「拾平台」今日晚上（15日）在社交網站發帖文，指「黃姐」早前透過勞工處外判中介，獲得首次面試機會，應徵公立醫院宿舍清潔雜工一職。惟今早跟指示到醫院表明身份欲見工時，男職員卻直言 「吓！請左人喇噃。」陪黃姐同行的「拾平台」成員ROY，替黃姐出示勞工處轉介的對話紀錄後，該男職員才請黃姐填寫長達4頁的表格。<br />\n<br />\n促羅致光推長者就業友善政策<br />\n<br />\n填表後，職員直言有關職位已聘到合適人選，卻仍然簡介該職位的工作內容；其後再表示X光部的清潔雜工今日通知會辭職，若該職位需要招聘，會再通知黃姐。黃姐直言：「約我來，問都未問就話請咗人，所以我覺得好愕然、好兒戲。」<br />\n<br />\n「拾平台」批評，長者能否成功就業，除了他們有否向勞工處求助，亦與僱主取態、工種及勞工福利相關，促羅致光推出完善的長者就業友善政策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/318417/%E6%8B%BE%E8%8D%92%E5%A9%A6%E9%BB%83%E5%A7%90%E8%81%BD%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%99%95-%E7%8D%B2%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E8%A6%8B%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%86%E6%9C%AA%E9%9D%A2%E8%A9%A6%E5%B7%B2%E7%84%A1%E7%A9%BA%E7%BC%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F318417%2F%25E6%258B%25BE%25E8%258D%2592%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A7%2590%25E8%2581%25BD%25E7%25BE%2585%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2599%2595-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%258E%2592%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%259C%25AA%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BC%25BA&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=124de33e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/318417/%E6%8B%BE%E8%8D%92%E5%A9%A6%E9%BB%83%E5%A7%90%E8%81%BD%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%99%95-%E7%8D%B2%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E8%A6%8B%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%86%E6%9C%AA%E9%9D%A2%E8%A9%A6%E5%B7%B2%E7%84%A1%E7%A9%BA%E7%BC%BA</a>"},{"pid":"22e4035d793eeb99b31f0fbf03bf128dedab37fc","tid":1108051,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e0bb2b7fd55281f2e92e47adc092cdbab0bf5f","tid":1108051,"uid":86509,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"何不食肉糜"},{"pid":"d307447c5fecbfe7a045c34a8e986947010cd909","tid":1108051,"uid":131622,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"落地獄<br />\n我睇完之後好想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca190b356e69c976ea8398448d83c395de6d0d40","tid":1108051,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"撚鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171ae6a1c85c8e101dfd649c002f82f59f772fd6","tid":1108051,"uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:44:19.000Z","msg":"車錢都蝕埋"},{"pid":"0908c6f91131c34e24056e69659adf1e9927fa07","tid":1108051,"uid":38651,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"d307447c5fecbfe7a045c